      "text": "アロハ～♪　こんな所で会うなんて奇遇やなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aloha! What a dang coincidence‚ meetin' like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.566666666666666,
      "endTime": 36.233333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 36.43333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "アロハは沖縄じゃない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They don’t say “aloha” in Okinawa…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.43333333333333,
      "endTime": 38.39999999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 38.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "うちはたまたまオフで沖縄に来てたんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I sometimes head down to Okinawa when I got some time off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.6,
      "endTime": 42,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2107_01_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "サニピの野外ライブのことは知ってたけど\nばったり会えるなんて、ほんまに奇遇やね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I knew 'bout Sunny Peace's outdoor show‚\nbut bumpin' into y'all like this is just a lucky break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.2,
      "endTime": 49,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 49.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
