      "text": "そうね……じゃあホテルに荷物を置いたら\nみんなで沖縄観光に行きましょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right‚ once we drop our bags off at the hotel‚\nlet’s head out for an Okinawan outing.",
        "id": ""
